 Incubus 将发行《Morning View》的重新录制版本https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-to-release-re-recorded-version-of-morning-view-3478595?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=incubus-to-release-re-recorded-早晨视图版本Emma WilkesSat, 05 Aug 2023 13:13:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3478595 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布兰登·博伊德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队还将于十月在好莱坞露天剧场完整演奏这张专辑</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-to-release-re-recorded-version-of-morning-view-3478595">Incubus 发布重录版《Morning View》的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="布兰登·博伊德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brandon-boyd-gina-wetzler-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/incubus">Incubus</a>准备重新录制他们 2001 年的开创性专辑“Morning View”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-brandon-boyd-talks-20-years-of-morning-view-we-wanted-to-change-our-environment-dramatically-3076106">Incubus 的布兰登·博伊德 (Brandon Boyd) 讲述 20 年来的《晨景》：“我们希望彻底改变我们的环境”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该唱片的新版本名为“Morning View XXIII”，将于 10 月 6 日通过乐队的新厂牌 Virgin Music 发行。</p><p>他们还计划于同一天在洛杉矶好莱坞露天剧场 (Hollywood Bowl) 举办一场演出来支持该片的上映，届时他们将完整表演《晨景》(Morning View)。 Paris Jackson 和 Action Bronson 将提供支持 - 您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到门票。</p><p> “我们很高兴与维珍合作发行<em>《Morning View XXIII》</em> ，我们迫不及待地想在好莱坞露天剧场为歌迷现场表演，”Incubus 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandon-boyd">布兰登·博伊德</a>在一份声明中表示。 “《 <em>Morning View XXIII》</em>将为我们的歌迷带来全新的歌曲体验，我们期待在 10 月 6 日发售时与大家分享！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="INCUBUS – 好莱坞露天剧场现场直播 – 10 月 6 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JTycyR1v4i8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Incubus <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-brandon-boyd-talks-20-years-of-morning-view-we-wanted-to-change-our-environment-dramatically-3076106">在 2021 年与<em>NME</em>谈论了《晨景》20 周年纪念日</a>。在谈到最初决定在马里布 Morning View Drive 的房子里录制这张专辑时，博伊德告诉<em>NME</em> ，乐队习惯了在“无风的软垫房间”中录制，希望在录制过程中不受干扰。</p><p> “我们决定不在传统环境中制作下一张专辑，因此我们在马里布租了这座远离一切的大空房子，”博伊德说。 “我们有兴趣看看，如果我们极大地改变我们的环境，一起在客厅里搭建，并将我们所有的装备都带进这所房子里，在那里你在那一刻尽可能不受干扰，会发生什么。”</p><p>除了提供宁静的休憩之所外，这座房子及其令人惊叹的周围环境也激发了专辑的一些内容。 “在那种截然相反的录音室里，从地板到天花板都有美丽如画的大教堂式窗户，大约 25 英尺高，真是太棒了，”博伊德说。</p><p> “我们必须看着一天的流逝，因为我们整天都在那里录制，然后在晚上，我们必须看着月亮过去，我们必须看着棕榈树在风中摇曳；有时我们会打开门，让大海的空气进入房间。这些东西会影响一切，尤其是当你处于创作过程中时。”</p><p>为了庆祝成立 20 周年，乐队回到马里布海滨别墅，在那里创作并录制了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-to-mark-20th-anniversary-of-morning-view-with-livestream-concert-3060736">整张唱片的现场直播音乐会</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/incubus-to-release-re-recorded-version-of-morning-view-3478595">Incubus 发布重录版《Morning View》的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
