 Sinéad O'Connor 去世后，她的音乐播放量增加了 2,885% https://www.nme.com/news/music/streams-of-sinead-oconnors-music-rise-by-2885-per-cent-following-her-death-3478549?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=streams-西尼德·奥康纳斯去世后，她的音乐数量上升了 2885%Damian Jones Sat, 05 Aug 2023 09:03:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3478549 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位音乐家兼活动家上个月在伦敦的家中去世</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/streams-of-sinead-oconnors-music-rise-by-2885-per-cent-following-her-death-3478549">《Sinéad O&#39;Connor 的音乐流》在她去世后上涨了 2,885%，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-inline-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">Sinéad O&#39;Connor</a>去世后，她的音乐播放量增加了 2,885%。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位音乐家兼活动家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">上个月（7 月 26 日）在伦敦的家中去世</a>，享年 56 岁。</p><p>此后，音乐界的许多人物都表达了敬意，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fall-out-boy-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474325">Fall Out Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-t">Ice-T</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-footage-tori-amos-covers-two-sinead-oconnor-songs-in-tribute-3474641">Tori Amos</a> 。</p><p>根据<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/sinead-oconnor-streams-surged-following-death/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard 的数据</a>，</em> 7 月 21 日至 27 日这一周，她的音乐在美国的播放量增加了 790 万次。</p><p> 7 月 24 日至 25 日期间，奥康纳的音乐被播放了 243,000 次，在她去世后，7 月 26 日至 27 日期间，该数字上升至 730 万次。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince 去世消息传出的一周内，仅她翻唱的 Prince</a>歌曲《Nothing Compares 2 U》就吸引了 320 万次观看。该单曲的下载量也达到了 10,000 次。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sinéad O&#39;Connor - Nothing Compares 2 U（官方音乐视频）[高清]" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0-EF60neguk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她的音乐在英国的流媒体数据尚未公布。</p><p>最新数据是在本周早些时候重新出现的<a href="https://people.com/sinead-o-connor-instructions-to-kids-to-protect-art-finances-upon-death-interview-exclusive-7566438" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>2021 年采访中发布的，奥康纳在采访中解释说，她考虑过保护自己的财务和艺术的重要性，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-told-children-to-call-my-accountant-before-emergency-services-in-event-of-her-death-3476253">指导她的孩子们在她去世后该怎么做</a>。</p><p> “看，当艺术家去世时，他们比他们活着时更有价值，”这位歌手当时说道。 “<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tupac">图帕克</a>去世后发行的专辑比他生前发行的专辑还要多，所以唱片公司的做法有点恶心。”</p><p>奥康纳继续说道：“这就是为什么我从孩子们还很小的时候就一直告诉他们，‘如果你的母亲明天去世了，在你拨打 911 之前，给我的会计师打电话，确保唱片公司不会开始泄露我的唱片。并且不告诉你钱在哪里’。”</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers)</a>最近透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phoebe-bridgers-shaved-her-head-in-high-school-to-look-like-sinead-oconnor-3477499">，她在高中时受到这位“革命性”艺术家的启发而剃了光头，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-crowe">罗素·克劳 (Russell Crowe)</a>也回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/russell-crowe-shares-chance-encounter-with-hero-sinead-oconnor-3476612">与这位已故歌手的一次偶然相遇</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/streams-of-sinead-oconnors-music-rise-by-2885-per-cent-following-her-death-3478549">《Sinéad O&#39;Connor 的音乐流》在她去世后上涨了 2,885%，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
